               <p>"Mother, a boy has stolen my beads;" I turned, and saw the prisoner running up Air-street; I had seen him at her side - he was stopped.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18220703-103-person893">
                  GEORGE 
                  PALMER
               <interp inst="t18220703-103-person893" type="surname" value="PALMER"></interp>
