               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18220703-103-person895">
                  SOPHIA 
                  TATE
               <interp inst="t18220703-103-person895" type="surname" value="TATE"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220703-103-person895" type="given" value="SOPHIA"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220703-103-person895" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am thirteen years old. I saw the prisoner at my side, and felt something against my neck; I turned round, he broke my necklace, and ran away with it. I am sure he is the boy. The gang got round the gentleman who stopped him, and he went away.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. She called out Stop that boy! I stopped immediately.</p>
